"""Tests for the compiled Cython simulation engine.

Phase 0: Runtime compilation, caching, and cache invalidation.
Phase 1: Codegen for continuous assigns, cross-validation.
Phase 2: Sequential logic — always @(posedge/negedge), always @(*),
         if/else, case, blocking/non-blocking assigns, NBA semantics.
Phase 3: LHS complexity (bit-select, range-select, concatenation) and
         memory arrays.
Phase 4: Timing fallback — initial blocks, always #delay, $display,
         VCD recording, ctx wrapper, cross-validation.
"""

